                        <interp inst="t18420509-name-547" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN SALISBURY</persName>
                  </hi>. I am the father of Thomas Salisbury. I received a bad sixpence from him—I kept it till I gave it up at the police-station.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18420509-name-548" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18420509-name-548" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18420509-name-548" type="surname" value="LONG"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18420509-name-548" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN LONG</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a policeman. I received a bad sixpence from Mr. Salisbury, and two pieces from Mr. Howell—I produce them.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18420509-name-549" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18420509-name-549" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18420509-name-549" type="surname" value="FIELD"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18420509-name-549" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>MR. JOHN FIELD</persName>
                  </hi>. The sixpence and the two pieces of a sixpence are all counterfeit.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> The last piece was passed from one to another, and was out of their sight.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18420509-name-550" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18420509-name-550" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18420509-name-550" type="surname" value="SALISBURY"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18420509-name-550" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>THOMAS SALISBURY</persName>
                  </hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined.</hi> It was passed round the shop to different people, but was not out of my sight.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner. Q.</hi> How do I know you might not have changed it? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> I am sure I did not.</p>
